{"id": "ChIJbZrTRzx-j4AR1AzhXfq8_4c", "rating": 4.7, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_INEXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 1378, "displayName": {"text": "Garden Creamery", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "A petite, pastel-toned scoop shop serving largely organic ice creams, sorbets & pops.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJbZrTRzx-j4AR1AzhXfq8_4c/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t4MFRYZDZkbGd3U0hOaWNIQnlVWFpmYWw5cWJuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "A small, minimalist ice cream shop with a modern vibe and an open kitchen feel where you can see everything being made, which adds to the experience.\n\nWe stopped by after dinner in the Mission, and the long line made it clear how popular this spot is. I tried the hojicha flavor, and it was exactly what I expected, a smooth, roasted tea flavor similar to matcha but deeper and more toasty. Really well done and consistent with what hojicha should taste like.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "A small, minimalist ice cream shop with a modern vibe and an open kitchen feel where you can see everything being made, which adds to the experience.\n\nWe stopped by after dinner in the Mission, and the long line made it clear how popular this spot is. I tried the hojicha flavor, and it was exactly what I expected, a smooth, roasted tea flavor similar to matcha but deeper and more toasty. Really well done and consistent with what hojicha should taste like.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Vash", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111600509426744294569/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlBjCO6gkA1mhk1zVBDzfmyLpX3YyurlMdnpEucy8svW-aFRUh=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-19T07:27:02.950403064Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t4MFRYZDZkbGd3U0hOaWNIQnlVWFpmYWw5cWJuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t4MFRYZDZkbGd3U0hOaWNIQnlVWFpmYWw5cWJuYxAB!2m1!1s0x808f7e3c47d39a6d:0x87ffbcfa5de10cd4"}, {"name": "places/ChIJbZrTRzx-j4AR1AzhXfq8_4c/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20weVVYSlBOMEp2Wm5sWVV6VkNlRTU2TW5oTGRGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I had a pretty good experience. They have great asian flavour. I tried a mix of Ube and something I can't recall now. Both were great. This is first time I tried Ube in ice cream and it was totally the highlight of my day.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I had a pretty good experience. They have great asian flavour. I tried a mix of Ube and something I can't recall now. Both were great. This is first time I tried Ube in ice cream and it was totally the highlight of my day.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kumar Vaibhav", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113383002468079500538/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_8P6jYC-Fa6CTJnmN2X-vonY87c6TN574rGS9FLsahAFKVC8T=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-07T05:04:47.334563722Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20weVVYSlBOMEp2Wm5sWVV6VkNlRTU2TW5oTGRGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20weVVYSlBOMEp2Wm5sWVV6VkNlRTU2TW5oTGRGRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f7e3c47d39a6d:0x87ffbcfa5de10cd4"}, {"name": "places/ChIJbZrTRzx-j4AR1AzhXfq8_4c/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkV05VOUVaek4zYkVsTWJXWlVRME5NWHpOb2RWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "Good ice cream with unusual flavors. Definitely worth going once, but not sure it warrants a second visit. The workers are very nice but it smelled like weed inside and it was extremely loud. It seems the kind of crowd it attracts is young for sure. The ice cream was good, not necessarily amazing. Glad we went, glad we tried it.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Good ice cream with unusual flavors. Definitely worth going once, but not sure it warrants a second visit. The workers are very nice but it smelled like weed inside and it was extremely loud. It seems the kind of crowd it attracts is young for sure. The ice cream was good, not necessarily amazing. Glad we went, glad we tried it.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Cristal Gamez", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102096211279429276788/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuHcCOMqIui9RQCjQTxJ-GRRljTw3D7n7ENlyzTnk6Y9YVf7xZ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-29T20:37:45.897397735Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkV05VOUVaek4zYkVsTWJXWlVRME5NWHpOb2RWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkV05VOUVaek4zYkVsTWJXWlVRME5NWHpOb2RWRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f7e3c47d39a6d:0x87ffbcfa5de10cd4"}, {"name": "places/ChIJbZrTRzx-j4AR1AzhXfq8_4c/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2toUFVDMVdjVGRFTFhaQ2NEbE9lRGgxVVVKMlVWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Me and my two kids saw some people on Valencia with delicious looking ice creams, followed their direction to Garden Creamery and were super impressed. They let us try a few and we enjoyed it all. Lil had had a sugar cone with ube and velvet chocolate on sugar cone, lil guy had cookies and cream with the strawberry ice cream and I had the salty Kaya and black sesame on a cake cone. When the guys strawberry started to fall they put in a cup for him. They were all super kind and it was a quick line. Yummy!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Me and 