dibly good, so creamy, and its vegan! the salty kaya's unique, almost reminiscent of a salted cream foam with a subtle hint of pandan/coconut. def recommend those two flavors!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "anthony", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113524490924128622709/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWaE6yGv1DNRETtHscGAdL27Q_vNcH_ZuWuSz7FjN0WSemE1jLI=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-07T23:57:48.915695905Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKck5teGhZMHN5WnpSUVEzWXRibFp6ZVdKNVJWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xKck5teGhZMHN5WnpSUVEzWXRibFp6ZVdKNVJWRRAB!2m1!1s0x808f7e3c47d39a6d:0x87ffbcfa5de10cd4"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJbZrTRzx-j4AR1AzhXfq8_4c/photos/AWCwydjfhebM-XRjCZZ-rxaiVkHU4fqLqaXTfS6FtWA3iX7ULi5jn3RjdvJj81_Bm3kEPRROpg0QmipmoebZ9L-GLuJeZlxpipO7U87ZUK35NuvSNMzFGuiwfIj8gRjiZEpz2dAJLfv-_JJVxS4YrJuHg2XpU6c2Mr22gazPMrrop7DyeSZinsBB3i7rCKAtgKn_ibquUxBI2fWBle7KNBVmcEj80s-kLEi2NR3K_fPg1nIZOyKlkLZTxz2Yh-PJD2wNAIZiUnxN24O8vBNxObDe_tPGg_aREONKpvf6aFXhqvTinxdzTnvgqh4RZUs9_q9S5mN-cAIM53RPZxZM_Rck6M7GSZUW6QXKaeOu9_aaSfp7DSGIAScwM2OzEJQ8ayjBfH1paI_gDu8-d87azaNSTXNtv4lIPrPGrnOmYeGsRZvFGE9JtNJJhCRoYtBnyA", "widthPx": 4032, "heightPx": 3024, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Manuela S.", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/113885901495547754076", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWW4sh1aPIO9hCJJj32c6hKgo7gkzrXEJHZaw3A7ld8naC-LVrU5g=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=!1e10!2sCIABIhBBuavMov99-jWXkau0UaIS&t=27&cb_client=maps_api_places.places_api&hl=en-US", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/place//data=!3m4!1e2!3m2!1sCIABIhBBuavMov99-jWXkau0UaIS!2e10!4m2!3m1!1s0x808f7e3c47d39a6d:0x87ffbcfa5de10cd4"}, {"name": "p